intro.lead:
This app helps you visualize trust between you and your child so they can clearly understand how it works.

Each action changes the trust level:
- when your child lies, 10 points are subtracted;
- when your child tells the truth, 5 points are added;
- when your child follows the repair steps, after completing the required steps 3 points are added.

This way, your child can see how their choices affect trust.
